{"tid":2333582,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple A14 比 Snapdragon 888 還要快　效能拋離一年","createTime":"2020-12-20T13:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T07:32:52.000Z","uid":105678,"like":61,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"44085a5f2307dd0f926bd38da19a3f4257bc6887","tid":2333582,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T13:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/888QRD_678x452.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F888QRD_678x452.jpg&h=f5a78f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQualcomm 最近公佈了最新的 Snapdragon 888 SoC 跑分成績，不過雖然它仍然要在 2021 年才會應用於智能手機，但分數仍然未及已經推出的 Apple A14 晶片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/116944.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F116944.jpeg&h=5a84de2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據 Qualcomm 分享的分數，Snapdragon 888 單線程分數為 1,135，多線程為 3,794。而根據同一個測試方式，Apple A14 的分數則分別為 1,603 和 4,187，仍然比 Snapdragon 888 高。而上一代 Apple A13 的單線程分數亦有 1,331，高於 Snapdragon 888。<br />\n<br />\n而在 GFXBench GPU 分數測試之中，Snapdragon 888 則落後於 Apple A13 和 A14。不過 AnandTech 認為如果計算耗電情況的話，Snapdragon 888 仍然有勝算。當然對用家而言，目前的晶片技術已經超越日常使用需要，因此用起來也不一定可以察覺到有太大分別。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAndroid行120Hz識飛又點，Iphone 12出先過S888效能都拋你一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇埋表發現原來Note 20U連成年前嘅iphone 11都未追到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3871e29a6236b51badee2955fe175fccc4888a7c","tid":2333582,"uid":196924,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T13:59:49.000Z","msg":"高通真係好撚廢...<br />\n<br />\n遲早變專利流氓"},{"pid":"01f95c1ecba2bb14b11042da86ea72a338168080","tid":2333582,"uid":43178,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"Snapdragon 888 則落後於 Apple A13 和 A14。<br />\n上年嘅A13都未追到？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce25c06086b3d9c3d926459118903baa514321b","tid":2333582,"uid":196924,"like":34,"dislike":4,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:02:31.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">目前的晶片技術已經超越日常使用需要</span><br />\n56k已足夠啲friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以Apple silicon可以用嚟推Macbook, 高通啲Windows機就垃圾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50079e1b36a3fb87cfeb2e5a677d47c233c266b3","tid":2333582,"uid":205522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"台積電win"},{"pid":"b0338a0561825326ef37b0edf212f56d22fa9ec1","tid":2333582,"uid":1524,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:06:28.000Z","msg":"In Apple， we trust。<br />\n不過點解Apple 請咗qualcom D人唔會比對家吿呢"},{"pid":"7b41318d23b85397b5a2f7b19e0846b40053a549","tid":2333582,"uid":72831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55b4c6f3717f1b7a9372e9470538a478e62fdb8","tid":2333582,"uid":196924,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"b0338a0561825326ef37b0edf212f56d22fa9ec1","tid":2333582,"uid":1524,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:06:28.000Z","msg":"In Apple， we trust。<br />\n不過點解Apple 請咗qualcom D人唔會比對家吿呢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:11:28.000Z","msg":"Qualcomm以前就話自己design<br />\n佢而家用ARM公版核心設計<br />\n所謂Kryo 585 Gold其實係Cortex-A77<br />\n可以點告人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1164395431053517438b971d9ad742d6f7eb15","tid":2333582,"uid":30857,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T14:14:59.000Z","msg":"快係快 但有咩用？<img src=\"/assets/